25 SUMMARY
2266 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, clarifies that the
2277 funding provided to the Maine Civil Legal Services Fund is intended to support civil legal
2288 services for low-income and elderly persons in the State. The amendment also adjusts the
2299 amount of appropriations in fiscal years 2025-26 and 2026-27.
